

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title>Error</title>
    <style>
        html, body, div, span, applet, object, iframe,
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, blockquote, pre,
        a, abbr, acronym, address, big, cite, code,
        del, dfn, em, img, ins, kbd, q, s, samp,
        small, strike, strong, sub, sup, tt, var,
        b, u, i, center,
        dl, dt, dd, ol, ul, li,
        fieldset, form, label, legend,
        table, caption, tbody, tfoot, thead, tr, th, td,
        article, aside, canvas, details, embed,
        figure, figcaption, main, footer, header, hgroup,
        menu, nav, output, ruby, section, summary,
        time, mark, audio, video {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 100%;
            font: inherit;
            vertical-align: baseline;
        }

        /* HTML5 display-role reset for older browsers */
        article, aside, main, details, figcaption, figure,
        footer, header, hgroup, menu, nav, section {
            display: block;
        }

        body {
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 0;
        }

        ol, ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        blockquote, q {
            quotes: none;
        }

            blockquote:before, blockquote:after,
            q:before, q:after {
                content: '';
                content: none;
            }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border-spacing: 0;
        }

        /* Clearfix class */

        .clearfix:after {
            content: ".";
            display: block;
            height: 0;
            clear: both;
            visibility: hidden;
        }

        #content-wrapper {
            width: auto;
        }

        #container {
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            width: 1230px;
            background-color: white;
            color: #84bd00;
        }

        #logo {
            height: 100%;
            float: left;
        }

        #logo-img {
            border: none;
        }

        #content {
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding-top: 115px;
            width: 500px;
        }

        #section1 {
            padding-bottom: 18.5px;
            width: 550px;
        }

        #bigText {
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: bold;
            float: left;
            padding-top: 130px;
            color:#84bd00;
        }

        #image {
            float: left;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .error-text {
            padding-top: 13px;
            text-align: left;
            clear: both;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color:#84bd00;
        }

        #section2 {
            padding-top: 6px;
            width: 500px;
            border-top: 1px solid #f3f8da;
        }

        .text {
            color: #7b868a;
            font-size: 19px;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 0 0 0;
        }

        .return-homepage-text {
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .homepage {
            color: #84bd00;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: left;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            .homepage:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="clearfix">
        <div id="container">
            <div id="logo">
                <a href="http://keepbritaintidy.org/home/481">
                   <img id="image1" width="130" height="110" title="" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
                </a>
            </div>

            <div id="content">
                <div id="section1">
                    <h2 id="bigText">Sorry,</h2>
                    <img id="image" width="97" height="162" title="" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
                    <h3 class="error-text">we seem to have put our foot in it.</h3>
                </div>
                <div id="section2">
                    <h3 class="text">We have taken note of this error.</h3>
                    <h3 class="text">Please give us a moment to tidy it up and try again in a few minutes.</h3>
                    <h3 class="text return-homepage-text">In the meantime please return to our <a class="homepage" href="/">homepage.</a></h3>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
